         <div xml:lang="gda">
            <p n="a#1" xml:space="preserve">Jek <persName><app><lem>Oleff</lem><rdg wit="#A">understregning begynder ved <q>e</q>, A</rdg></app> Bille</persName> aff <placeName><app><lem>Æble[t]huedh</lem><rdg wit="#A">understregning slutter ved <q>u</q>, A; <q>t</q> utydeligt</rdg></app></placeName> aff wapn ku<ex>n</ex>gør th<ex>et</ex> alle mæn . at so som min
      <app><lem>moth<ex>e</ex>r</lem><rdg wit="#A">her begynder understregning, A</rdg></app> <persName>Cecilie <app><lem>Tyghesdot<ex>er</ex></lem><rdg wit="#A">her slutter understregning, A</rdg></app></persName> hu<ex>n</ex> hau<ex>er</ex>
      saalt oc skiøt h<ex>e</ex>r <persName>Jwen Bryseke</persName> alle sinæ gotz . he<ex>n</ex>nis
      eghit fæth<ex>e</ex>rnis oc møthernis gotz . th<ex>et</ex> halder jec stathut
      j alle madhe / ♦ Oc ke<ex>n</ex>nis jec enge<ex>n</ex> ræt / ell<ex>e</ex>r
      ydermer<ex>e</ex> tiltale athaue til the gotz som <app><lem>[j]</lem><rdg wit="#A">utydeligt, A</rdg></app> h<ex>e</ex>r Jwens breff
      sta . ♦</p>
            <p n="a#2" xml:space="preserve">In cujus rei testimonium sigillum meum una cum sigillis virorum discretorum videlicet
        <persName><app><lem>Ni<damage>colai I</damage>nguers<ex>øn</ex></lem><rdg wit="#A">suppleret efter Gammeldanske Diplomer</rdg></app></persName> de
        <placeName>Nesby</placeName> / <persName>Ottonis Foss</persName>
      <persName>Gerekini Diegn</persName> et <persName>Jacobi Nicolai</persName> de
        <placeName>Otestørp</placeName> presentibus est <app><lem>appe<damage>nsum</damage></lem><rdg wit="#A">suppleret efter Gammeldanske Diplomer</rdg></app> ♦</p>
